-- Countrywide Investors Said to Reach $600 Million Class-Action Settlement
-- Edvard Pettersson
-- 2010-04-23T23:21:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-23/countrywide-investors-said-to-reach-600-million-class-action-settlement.html

          
          
             Countrywide Financial Corp.
investors, led by two New York pension funds, have reached a
settlement of their class-action lawsuit valued at more than
$600 million, a person familiar with the case said.
